com.centurylink.mdw.workflow.activity.event

Class WaitActivityFallback

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.centurylink.mdw.workflow.activity.event.WaitActivityFallback
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RegisteredService, StartupService
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DependenciesFallbackPublish, TimerWaitFallback

    public abstract class WaitActivityFallback
extends java.lang.Object
implements StartupService
    Periodically queries waiting activities to perform fallback processing to fix stuck instances. Check interval is specified on the Configurator Events tab (see getCheckIntervalAttribute()). Activity pagelet needs to be updated accordingly.
